Package: scryAnotherDay
Title: A wrapper for the Scryfall API
Version: 0.0.0.1000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Joshua",
           family = "de la Bruere",
           role = c("cre", "aut"),
           email = "joshua@delabj.com")
Description: A R interface to the Scryfall REST API.  
    Scryfall provides a database of Magic The Gathering Cards with related
    information. This package serves as a wrapper to the Scryfall API and 
    is not endorsed or supported by Scryfall.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/delabj/scryfallR
